@page "/experience/kivi"
<h3>KIVI TV</h3>
<div class="mt-5">
    <h2 class="mb-4">
        <i class="bi bi-tv m-2"></i>Kivi Tv AOSP development: Update, Launcher, Remote control apps.
    </h2>

    <div>
        <h4>Overview</h4>
        <p><strong>Industry:</strong> Smart TV Manufacturing</p>
        <p><strong>Founded:</strong> 2016</p>
        <p><strong>Headquarters:</strong> Kyiv, Ukraine</p>
        <p>
            <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://kivismart.com" target="_blank">KIVI</a>
        </p>

        <h4>About</h4>
        <p>KIVI is an international smart TV brand recognized for its innovative products and services. The company has sold over 1.5 million devices across more than 20 countries, including markets in Europe and Asia. KIVI TVs are certified by Google and Netflix, offering users access to premium content and features.</p>
       
        <p>
            At Kivi.TV, I was extensively involved in customizing TV software to deliver smart TV solutions for the European market. My core responsibility was modifying and optimizing the Android Open Source Project (AOSP) to meet regional standards and enhance the user experience.
        </p>

        <ul>
            <li><strong>Custom Launcher Development:</strong> Led the design of a custom launcher featuring integrated recommendations, activity tracking, and user-centric navigation. Required deep understanding of the Android Framework, System UI, LauncherApps, PackageManager, and content providers.</li>

            <li><strong>System Update Mechanism:</strong> Implemented a robust OTA (Over-The-Air) and APK update system. This included backend communication, incremental update application using <code>update_engine</code>, payload management, and rollback safety mechanisms.</li>

            <li><strong>Low-Level System Configuration:</strong> Configured system settings using <code>build.prop</code>, <code>init.rc</code>, and property overrides. Managed root access, vendor keys, APK signing, and verified boot requirements for platform integrity.</li>

            <li><strong>Tooling & Automation:</strong> Developed Bash scripts to automate APK installs, logging, reboots, and configuration tasks â€” significantly accelerating development, testing, and deployment processes.</li>

            <li><strong>Kivi Remote App Integration:</strong> Built a two-way mobile-TV communication system enabling users to control TV settings from smartphones. Utilized Android TV Input Framework (TIF), AIDL for IPC, and TV Input Manager for hardware interfacing.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

